txt.en: 'Who dares come into my lair?  Who dares take away my children?'
'Mistress, grant me your wisdom!'
'You can not stop Her Army!  I will not allow it!'
'You come here and you wish to destroy that which you do not understand.'
'Your ignorance will be your final undoing!'
'The light... it dims... what are you doing?  I must protect myself!'
'Welcome.  You will all know the Mistress' gift very shortly.'
'You are too strong!  Too many!  It is good I am here to stop you!'
'What is this?  The Mistress ordered me not to fail!  Death to all!'
'You will taste of my rage for what you've done to my brother!'
'Now, we fight.'
Once the Mistress of Pestilence is killed, you may use this chest.
'The Mistress' Army is too strong!  We were bred stronger and tougher!'
'Darklings, arise!'
'I gather the shadows!'
'Flagit, I take your strength'
'MORE...'
'ROCKS!'
'Mistress, lend me your courage!'
'You will not stop the Mistress' plan!  Globsnaga stop you!'
Once the Blind-One is killed, you can use this chest.
'Mistress, give me your strength!'
'His death will mean your death!'
'What is stopping you?'
'Inside!  Now!'
'Move, filthy animal!'
'Come, troll!  You are the Mistress' now.'
Once Zholuga is killed, you can use this chest.
'Zholuga, bend to my will.'
'Mistress, grant me your protection!'
'Be careful!  It still does not know it belongs to the Mistress now.'
'Watch yourselves!  The Mistress will not tolerate failure!'
Once Istum is killed, you can use this chest.
'You work for the Mistress now!'
'Work harder, pitiful wretch!'
'You will meet the Mistress soon, Globsnaga.'
Hi!
Once Flagit is killed, you can use this chest.
'Let darkness aid me!'
'Impressive.  Your thoughts are clear but you still do not see.'
'You have made it deep into our lair.  The Mistress will be most displeased if I allow you any further.'
Once Rung and Blagh are killed, you may use this chest.
'Istum, your power is mine.'
